node.text: Thank you to @hisbrownpoet for creating this amazing video featuring Sudio Ett! We are proud to celebrate our black creatives/collaborators 🎶

node.text: Fall is around the corner here in Sweden and we are waving goodbye to summer for now this year🌊👋🏻 What did you guys do this summer with your Sudio earphones?😊 @anabenedcto #sudio #shapingsound

node.text: Starting the week off stylish with Ett Anthracite 😎🎶 What's on your playlist today? @enjoytroy @sandaire29 #sudio #shapingsound

We are always happy to hear how much you like the design of our Sudio products☺️ Does Ett Anthracite go well with your style or would you pick a different color? @interiorbyjulias #sudio #shapingsound

It's finally weekend, everyone! Gloomy weather here in Stockholm but luckily we have Nio green to make our Saturday a much better one ☺️ What are your plans this weekend? @simplymadhoo #sudio #shapingsound
